---
<section class="stack-section">
  <div class="stack-inner">
    <div class="stack-text">
      <p class="section-label">How I build</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">The same stack.<br/>Refined over time.</h2>
      <p class="section-body">Six years of shipping production code taught me to settle on tools that move fast without piling up debt. TypeScript everywhere, NestJS on the server, and abstractions only when they earn their keep.</p>
      <ul class="stack-list">
        <li><span class="check">✓</span> <strong>TypeScript-first</strong>: types are documentation that never goes stale</li>
        <li><span class="check">✓</span> <strong>NestJS on the server</strong>: typed modules and DI that scale cleanly</li>
        <li><span class="check">✓</span> <strong>React where it earns it</strong>: only when interactivity justifies the runtime</li>
        <li><span class="check">✓</span> <strong>AI with discipline</strong>: phased, documented, reviewed, never one-shot guesses</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/blog" class="stack-cta">Read how I think about engineering →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="stack-code">
      <div class="code-window">
        <div class="code-header">
          <span class="code-lang">TypeScript</span>
          <span class="code-file">src/posts/posts.controller.ts</span>
        </div>
        <pre class="code-body"><code><span class="ck">import</span> <span class="cv">&#123; Controller, Get &#125;</span> <span class="ck">from</span> <span class="cs">'@nestjs/common'</span>
<span class="ck">import</span> <span class="cv">&#123; PostsService &#125;</span> <span class="ck">from</span> <span class="cs">'./posts.service'</span>

<span class="cc">@</span><span class="cv">Controller</span>(<span class="cs">'posts'</span>)
<span class="ck">export class</span> <span class="cv">PostsController</span> &#123;
  <span class="ck">constructor</span>(<span class="ck">private readonly</span> posts<span class="ck">:</span> <span class="cv">PostsService</span>) &#123;&#125;

  <span class="cc">@</span><span class="cv">Get</span>()
  findAll()<span class="ck">:</span> <span class="cv">Promise</span>&lt;<span class="cv">Post</span>[]&gt; &#123;
    <span class="ck">return</span> <span class="cv">this</span>.posts.findAll()
  &#125;
&#125;</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .stack-section { padding: var(--space-section) var(--space-xl); background: var(--color-canvas); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline); }
  .stack-inner { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-section); align-items: center; }
  .section-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.88px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
  .section-heading { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); letter-spacing: -1.08px; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); }
  .section-body { font-size: 15px; color: var(--color-body); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-xl); }
  .stack-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 var(--space-xl); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-sm); }
  .stack-list li { font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-body); line-height: 1.5; display: flex; gap: var(--space-sm); align-items: flex-start; }
  .stack-list li strong { color: var(--color-ink); font-weight: 600; }
  .check { color: var(--color-ink); font-weight: 600; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .stack-cta { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-text-link); text-decoration: none; }
  .stack-cta:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .code-window { background: var(--color-surface-dark); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
  .code-header { background: var(--color-surface-dark-elevated); padding: 10px 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-sm); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
  .code-lang { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #47c2ff; }
  .code-file { font-size: 12px; color: #555; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; margin-left: auto; }
  .code-body { margin: 0; padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-xl); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; background: transparent; color: var(--color-on-dark); border-radius: 0; overflow-x: auto; }
  .code-body code { all: unset; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; }
  .ck { color: #c792ea; }
  .cv { color: #82aaff; }
  .cs { color: #c3e88d; }
  .cc { color: #546e7a; font-style: italic; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .stack-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-xxl); } }
  @media (max-width: 640px) { .stack-section { padding: var(--space-section) var(--space-base); } .section-heading { font-size: 28px; } }
</style>
